        <activityName xml:lang="en">electricity, high voltage, production mix</activityName>
        <generalComment>
          <text xml:lang="en" index="0">The shares of electricity technologies on this market are valid for the year 2021. The shares have been calculated based on statistics from 2021: IEA World Energy Statistics and Balances. OECD iLibrary, eISSN: 1683-4240, DOI: 10.1787/enestats-data-en and US EPA: Emissions &amp; Generation Resource Integrated Database, https://www.epa.gov/energy/emissions-generation-resource-integrated-database-egrid. Grid losses and imports are based on data from 2020 (also IEA World Energy Statistics and Balances).</text>
        </generalComment>
      </activity>
      <geography geographyId="f37ced82-5df8-48c2-a207-1e36dd11a112">
        <shortname xml:lang="en">US-WECC</shortname>
